305610ae" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" =
style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wi=
dth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgro=
und-color: #ccc;">Microsoft was shocked Friday</a> when it received just a =
few minutes notice=E2=80=9D of the firing, despite having invested <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33431564.256422/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTEtMTkvb3BlbmFpLW5lZ290=
aWF0aW9ucy10by1yZWluc3RhdGUtYWx0bWFuLWhpdC1zbmFnLW92ZXItYm9hcmQtcm9sZT9jbXB=
pZD1CQkQxMTIwMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2=
xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzExMjAmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8=
524a319a23cB1840730c" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">  some $13 billion</a> in OpenAI. Other inves=
tors and employees were similarly blindsided. But that=E2=80=99s the deal! =
The board decides, and it does not answer to the investors or employees or =
take their interests into account. Its only concern is with =E2=80=9Chumani=
ty.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Except that then OpenAI spent the weekend back=
tracking and trying to hire Altman back, under pressure from Microsoft Corp=
., other investors and employees. Altman=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.=
mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33431564.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZX=
JnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTEtMTkvb3BlbmFpLW5lZ290aWF0aW9ucy10by1yZ=
Wluc3RhdGUtYWx0bWFuLWhpdC1zbmFnLW92ZXItYm9hcmQtcm9sZT9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMTIwMjNf=
TU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGV=
