1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; ba=
ckground-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[11]</span>
</a></p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand, if the story here is =E2=80=
=9COpenAI=E2=80=99s board of directors found a Rogue Capitalism at OpenAI, =
and moved to kill it before it could destroy their nice nonprofit mission,=
=E2=80=9D well, it=E2=80=99s also not clear that that worked. (It=E2=80=99s=
 not clear that it=E2=80=99s true, either:=C2=A0Shear <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33431564.256422/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmN=
