th: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgrou=
nd-color: #ccc;">tweeted this morning</a>=C2=A0that =E2=80=9Cthe board did =
*not* remove Sam over any specific disagreement on safety, their reasoning =
was completely different from that. I=E2=80=99m not crazy enough to take th=
is job without board support for commercializing our awesome models.=E2=80=
=9D) Capitalism, like the metaphorical superintelligent robot, is pretty cr=
afty. If the board killed the Rogue Capitalism at OpenAI, it will pop up ag=
ain elsewhere.=C2=A0=E2=80=9CAhahaha you fools,=E2=80=9D say=C2=A0Microsoft=
 and the OpenAI employees and, like, the abstract concept of Silicon Valley=
 startup investing generally. =E2=80=9CYou trusted in the formalities of co=
